denounce the government opposition church groups also called for 
peaceful protests 
police remained on nationwide alert and riot squads stood guard 
at key locations in seoul or waited out of sight in side streets 
protesters have denounced the united states in demonstrations 
this week charging that washington supports military dictatorship 
in south korea 
leaders of the radical students who represent an important 
campus minority want seoul to end its alliance with washington and 
expel the 40000 us troops based in south korea 
