invention a computerized machine designed to evaluate and 
rehabilitate the lower back 
jones donation of 847 million was announced at a morning news 
conference at his 500acre ranch near ocala 
i have a longstanding interest in physical training and 
wellness and my support of the university of florida will boost 
the research of lower back pain one of mans most nagging 
problems jones said 
