in a us court he was identified as belonging to the medellin 
cartel a group of colombians who control cocaine smuggling into 
the united states 
a 1979 treaty says no colombian extradited to the united states 
can be sentenced to more than the maximum penalty 30 years in 
this case that the defendant would have faced in colombia 
after lehder was extradited last year colombias supreme court 
